channel.title: All My Runescape Deobs and Originals (194, 317-377)
channel.description:
Here they are, and from 355 up I kept the original, binary, and source jars, before that they are all from waffendennis (194 original is from krichevskoy).
I am also uploading the 317 deob modified just enough to connect to private servers separately, because a lot of people want it.
If anyone has more (or any originals) that I don't have please post them.
These are all for educational purposes only :|, have fun ;)
[url=https://www.moparisthebest.com/downloads/deobs.tar.gz]All Deobs[/url]
[url=https://www.moparisthebest.com/downloads/RuneScape_317_PRIV.jar]RuneScape_317_PRIV.jar[/url]
(to allow the 317 private client to load the new cache, look at bentski's thread [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,129.0.html]here[/url])
